{"tid":2122473,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲: 王室的坦白","createTime":"2020-07-24T04:21:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T14:06:22.000Z","uid":21493,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d410b19c3cd76384d21ac051ab4149f7d92af5d4","tid":2122473,"uid":21493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:21:52.000Z","msg":"陳雲：王室的坦白。<br />\n荷蘭國王威廉坦白講：「冠狀病毒是假新聞。」<br />\n與兩位公主拍照，有人提醒要1.5距離。<br />\n（荷蘭文Maar dit is 1.5 meter .）<br />\n國王說：「假新聞，不是嗎？」<br />\n（Fake news, h&egrave;?）<br />\n公主說：「爸爸，你不可以這樣說話的。」<br />\n（荷蘭文：Dat kan je niet zeggen, papa .）<br />\n按：荷蘭朋友傳給大家看的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef98e19de5857ab88ea00f1c17f645b31d6277c3","tid":2122473,"uid":273703,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:23:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc376332ce1a802623ff0c45e15419e061f757ec","tid":2122473,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef98e19de5857ab88ea00f1c17f645b31d6277c3","tid":2122473,"uid":273703,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:23:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:24:31.000Z","msg":"P牌仔你拉撚到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5624b9a85c478e083f8cf8fca5ab8d1dd5d5d87c","tid":2122473,"uid":21493,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:24:49.000Z","msg":"陳雲又中<br />\n<br />\n瘋火輸出動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" cl